For the search 
1.Retrieve the data from the firestore database when the page loads.
2.Save all the data in a json object
3.when the user enters a search query and clicks the the button, implement a function that triggers on onCLick that will take the query, loop through
the JSON object, and filter using a filtering algorithm.
4.display the filtered data

For the submit offer
1.when the user on submit, get the value of each input box
2. retreive the Broker information from the firestore
2.use an API and call GET with the value and parameters to send the data to the Notification API to send a notification to the broker
